md","line":107},{"title":"【来源】 ","target":"../【来源】.md","line":112},{"title":"【知识点】  ","target":"../【知识点】.md","line":112},{"title":"【中档】  ","target":"../【中档】.md","line":112},{"title":"【来源】 ","target":"../【来源】.md","line":134},{"title":"【中档】  ","target":"../【中档】.md","line":134},{"title":"【知识点】  ","target":"../【知识点】.md","line":135},{"title":"值域","target":"../值域.md","line":171},{"title":"判别式法,方程有解问题的转化.","target":"函数框架梳理/三要素/值域/判别式法,方程有解问题的转化.md","line":201},{"title":"单变量","target":"../单变量.md","line":211},{"title":"定义域","target":"../定义域.md","line":229},{"title":"分式函数","target":"../分式函数.md","line":250},{"title":"▲","target":"../▲.md","line":254},{"title":"【来源】 ","target":"../【来源】.md","line":263},{"title":"【中档】  ","target":"../【中档】.md","line":263},{"title":"【知识点】  ","target":"../【知识点】.md","line":264},{"title":"分式函数","target":"../分式函数.md","line":264},{"title":"\\frac{15}{8}, +\\infty)$； (2) $(-\\frac{1}{2}, \\frac{3}{4})$。(3) $\\left(\\frac{36}{31}, \\frac{16}{13}\\right)$\n            - 解析： (1)\n                - 令$t = \\sqrt{x - 1} (t \\geq 0)$，则$x = t^2 + 1$，代入得$f(t) = 2(t^2 + 1) - t = 2t^2 - t + 2$；\n                - 转化为二次函数求值域：$f(t) = 2(t - \\frac{1}{4})^2 + \\frac{15}{8}$，对称轴为$t = \\frac{1}{4}$，开口向上，当$t = \\frac{1}{4}$时取最小值$\\frac{15}{8}$，故值域为$[\\frac{15}{8}, +\\infty)$。 (2)\n                - 分离常数：$f(x) = \\frac{2(x + 1) - 5}{x + 1} = 2 - \\frac{5}{x + 1}$；\n                - 分析单调性：$y = \\frac{5}{x + 1}$在$(1, 3)$上单调递减，故$y = -\\frac{5}{x + 1}$在$(1, 3)$上单调递增，$f(x) = 2 - \\frac{5}{x + 1}$单调递增；\n                - 代入端点值：$f(1) = 2 - \\frac{5}{2} = -\\frac{1}{2}$，$f(3) = 2 - \\frac{5}{4} = \\frac{3}{4}$，故值域为$(-\\frac{1}{2}, \\frac{3}{4})$。\n            - 【理解】\n                - (1) 换元法通过将根式转化为二次函数，实现 “复杂函数简单化”，需注意新变量的非负性，体现了 “转化与化归” 思想；\n                - (2) 分离常数法将一次分式函数拆解为 “常数 + 分式”，通过分析分式的单调性求值域，是一次分式函数值域的典型解法，体现了 “结构分析与单调性应用” 的思维。\n        - \n        - \n        - \n        - > [【压轴】  ","target":"../【压轴】.md","line":269},{"title":"【来源】 ","target":"../【来源】.md","line":282},{"title":"【知识点】  ","target":"../【知识点】.md","line":283},{"title":"存在任意","target":"../存在任意.md","line":283},{"title":"处理式子","target":"../处理式子.md","line":294},{"title":"值域","target":"../值域.md","line":295},{"title":"1例题","target":"../1题目.md","line":301},{"title":"处理式子","target":"../处理式子.md","line":301},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/XdxEaXJQ8-2KZ8u_BJW3SDwgMfzJ5OnPnXNcQY5uZ9Bt_vDOvdYpxkddXe_pUwx1AbQDAJEZJqiUg0E6udg4yrSiL_6_3un4RItiaznH3F3nru6z7xTQabhXQAa_-x7I.png","target":"../高一数学寒假-01函数综合（一）/Highlights/Page 09/Untitled.md","line":302},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/9DCtjmYXznM-azk_0Yr-VRTKadVcUT_QFafGYYTKfd1FxmlPe1HCWmjGuXCym2w3mTFvpoJyeiOE8LNm-N5EHdso-nCZPuDbc_VEMEHPRIZ3jXdyll1Xw87BmsddhEsB.png","target":"../高一数学寒假-01函数综合（一）/Highlights/Page 10/Untitled.md","line":303},{"title":"1例题","target":"../1题目.md","line":306},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/dBIhupBNsoC6InpPKxWuQfofM8PBwDBOg9k-mZGmvxlv4pL1ADtGAvs30ZlR5sAA2DRgk_WKZ-OdOsSJsAUvlwIn0mBTVGVxKTPI7hJn13CsKmDx6b6MfZ56UrXsJDil.png","target":"../高一数学寒假-01函数综合（一）/Highlights/Page 11/Untitled.md","line":308},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/HGCPd5tKOGY2sut5pRuFzYbU-9v_7-rRmeoCI-0rGBOYs9UZRhsqVTohcPmx9Hu53ArY05qxD4C0WBqQQ9jTS5HEXdwifzPxA5PDAeRcfbyOoK4NZs7GFPrLA5zYnhLS.png","target":"../高一数学寒假-01函数综合（一）/Highlights/Page 13/Untitled.md","line":309},{"title":"距离","target":"../距离.md","line":311},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/3GGIYdclFDLAwKvUlnXw2leYPMvP3jpkPjpkjkJKV0hQx82Q6E98OoFLL9rqVKiReAnSSpQexFLm8-LLOqHnACHiSGpE7EMJY15JASfrKRnZ4qxfHfL-e2x_U0QmNkco.png","target":"../高一数学寒假-01函数综合（一）/Highlights/Page 06/Untitled.md","line":312},{"title":"https://remnote-user-data.s3.amazonaws.com/fEUHGN8Puc_Tk3ZXsGdjFQHMzKhV0XYnqqHJhOfAiFhWgbOIlehbmnSFb7alGODiLGbXkl750z6sRqMJ6RRbu7xJbouM-Ethq4eQItXr-fcgMb-qx6DGhO2jkeblZwoN.png","target":"../高一数学寒假-01函数综合（一）/Highlights/Page 07/Untitled.md","line":313}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed"